The "Minimum Commitment Period" is 36 month(s).

The license includes up to 1000000 Visits (as Visits is defined in the Agreement) per month.

Licensee is permitted to use Sitecore Software on a total of 4 Non-Production Server installation(s) (as that term defined in the Agreement).
